ica orthography)" lang="be-tarask" hreflang="be-tarask" class="interlanguage-link-target">Беларуская (тарашкевіца)</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-bg"><a href="https://bg.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9E%D0%B4%D0%B8%D1%81%D0%B5%D0%B0%D1%81_%D0%95%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%81" title="Одисеас Елитис — bulgare" lang="bg" hreflang="bg" class="interlanguage-link-target">Български</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-br"><a href="https://br.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odysseas_Elytis" title="Odysseas Elytis — breton" lang="br" hreflang="br" class="interlanguage-link-target">Brezhoneg</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ca"><a href="https://ca.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odisseus_Elitis" title="Odisseus Elitis — catalan" lang="ca" hreflang="ca" class="interlanguage-link-target">Català</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-cs"><a href="https://cs.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odysseas_Elytis" title="Odysseas Elytis — tchèque" lang="cs" hreflang="cs" class="interlanguage-link-target">Čeština</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-da"><a href="https://da.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odysseas_Elytis" title="Odysseas Elytis — danois" lang="da" hreflang="da" class="interlanguage-link-target">Dansk</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-de"><a href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odysseas_Elytis" title="Odysseas Elytis — allemand" lang="de" hreflang="de" class="interlanguage-link-target">Deutsch</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-el"><a href="https://el.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CE%9F%CE%B4%CF%85%CF%83%CF%83%CE%AD%CE%B1%CF%82_%CE%95%CE%BB%CF%8D%CF%84%CE%B7%CF%82" title="Οδυσσέας Ελύτης — grec" lang="el" hreflang="el" class="interlanguage-link-target">Ελληνικά</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-en"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odysseas_Elytis" title="Odysseas Elytis — anglais" lang="en" hreflang="en" class="interlanguage-link-target">English</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-eo"><a href="https://eo.wikipedia.org/wiki