<ul><li><span class="ouvrage" id="yi">Yannis E. Ioannou, «&#160;<cite style="font-style:normal;">Vers une esthétique méditerranéenne (?) Actes du colloque tenu à Lyon, 1997, Université Lumière-Lyon 2, Université de Chypre</cite>&#160;», <i>Chypre et la Méditerranée orientale, Maison de l’Orient et de la Méditerranée Jean Pouilloux</i>, <abbr class="abbr" title="volume">vol.</abbr>&#160;31,&#8206; <time>2000</time>, <abbr class="abbr" title="page(s)">p.</abbr>&#160;163-171 <small style="line-height:1em;">(<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.persee.fr/doc/mom_1274-6525_2000_act_31_1_1855">lire en ligne</a>, consulté le <span class="nowrap">5 avril 2020</span>)</small><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Vers+une+esth%C3%A9tique+m%C3%A9diterran%C3%A9enne+%28%3F%29+Actes+du+colloque+tenu+%C3%A0+Lyon%2C+1997%2C+Universit%C3%A9+Lumi%C3%A8re-Lyon+2%2C+Universit%C3%A9+de+Chypre&amp;rft.jtitle=Chypre+et+la+M%C3%A9diterran%C3%A9e+orientale%2C+Maison+de+l%E2%80%99Orient+et+de+la+M%C3%A9diterran%C3%A9e+Jean+Pouilloux&amp;rft.au=Yannis+E.+Ioannou&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.volume=31&amp;rft.pages=163-171&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Ffr.wikipedia.org%3AOdyss%C3%A9as+El%C3%BDtis"></span></span>.</li></ul>
<dl><dt>Ouvrages</dt></dl>
<ul><li><span class="ouvrage" id="class=&quot;lang-el&quot;_lang=&quot;el&quot;&gt;Παναγιώτα_Τεμπρίδου2016"><span class="ouvrage" id="Παναγιώτα_Τεμπρίδου2016"><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : grec moderne">(el)</abbr> <span class="lang-el" lang="el">Παναγιώτα Τεμπρίδου</span>, <cite style="font-style:normal" lang="el"><span class="lang-el" lang="el">Το άμοιαστο της ποίησης και το ισόποσο της φιλοσοφίας&#160;: ο διπλός εαυτός του Οδυσσέα Ελύτη</span></cite>, Thessalonique, Université Aristote de Thessalonique,&#8206; <time>2016</time>, 576&#160;<abbr class="abbr" title="pages">p.</abbr>, Thèse <small style="line-height:1em;">(<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://thesis.ekt.gr/thesisBookReader/id/37447#page/1/mode/2up">lire en ligne</a>)</small><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%CE%A4%CE%BF+%CE%AC%CE%BC%CE%BF%CE%B9%CE%B1%CF%83%CF%84%CE%BF+%CF%84%CE%B7%CF%82+%CF%80%CE%BF%CE%AF%CE%B7%CF%83%CE%B7%CF%82+%CE%BA%CE%B1%CE%B9+%CF%84%CE%BF+%CE%B9%CF%83%CF%8C%CF%80%CE%BF%CF%83%CE%BF+%CF%84%CE%B7%CF%82+%CF%86%CE%B9%CE%BB%CE%BF%CF%83%CE%BF%CF%86%CE%AF%CE%B1%CF%82+%3A+%CE%BF+%CE%B4%CE%B9%CF%80%CE%BB%CF%8C%CF%82+%CE%B5%CE%B1%CF%85%CF%84%CF%8C%CF%82+%CF%84%CE%BF%CF%85+%CE%9F%CE%B4%CF%85%CF%83%CF%83%CE%AD%CE%B1+%CE%95%CE%BB%CF%8D%CF%84%CE%B7&amp;rft.place=Thessalonique&amp;rft.pub=Universit%C3%A9+Aristote+de+Thessalonique&amp;rft.au=%3Cspan+class%3D%22lang-el%22+lang%3D%22el%22%3E%CE%A0%CE%B1%CE%BD%CE%B1%CE%B3%CE%B9%CF%8E%CF%84%CE%B1+%CE%A4%CE%B5%CE%BC%CF%80%CF%81%CE%AF%CE%B4%CE%BF%CF%85%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.date=2016&amp;rft.tpages=576&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Ffr.wikipedia.org%3AOdyss%C3%A9as+El%C3%BDtis"></span></span></span></li>
